snippet.title: Longvinter | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
After 3 years of game development, growing as company, bug fixes and community suggestions and engagement, Longvinter has now been released with the 1.0 Update.

Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1635450/Longvinter/

Longvinter will be releasing on PlayStation next year!
